{{自杀}}
'''[[自殺|自殺]]在[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]'''是一個顯著的社會問題。俄羅斯是自殺率最高的國家之一，在[[蘇聯解體|蘇聯解體]]至2011年10月已有近百萬名俄國人自殺<ref name="Nearly a million Russians have committed suicide since collapse of Soviet Union">{{cite news|title=Nearly a million Russians have committed suicide since collapse of Soviet Union|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2052156/Nearly-million-Russians-committed-suicide-collapse-Soviet-Union.html|accessdate=14 January 2013|newspaper=Mail Online|location=London|first=Lucy|last=Buckland|date=22 October 2011|archive-date=2014-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141211051708/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2052156/Nearly-million-Russians-committed-suicide-collapse-Soviet-Union.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>；研究人員指自殺問題與{{link-en|俄羅斯酒精使用情況|Alcohol consumption in Russia}}存在密切的關聯<ref name="Heavy Drinking and Suicide in Russia">{{cite web|title=Heavy Drinking and Suicide in Russia|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC1642767/pdf/nihms11269.pdf|publisher=National Institutes of Health|accessdate=14 January 2013|archive-date=2021-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211007115921/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC1642767/pdf/nihms11269.pdf}}</ref>。

== 數據 ==
在2012年，俄羅斯1906335宗死亡個案中，有29735宗（1.56%）為自殺<ref name="gks">{{Cite web |url=http://www.gks.ru/wps/wcm/connect/rosstat_main/rosstat/ru/statistics/population/demography/ |title=Демография::Федеральная служба государственной статистики |access-date=2014-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140204212420/http://www.gks.ru/wps/wcm/connect/rosstat_main/rosstat/ru/statistics/population/demography/ |archive-date=2014-02-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。俄羅斯的自殺率在於90年代中後期達到高峰後一直穩步下降：當時每10萬人有40人死於自殺，在2001年到2006年下降了30％<ref name="WHO Russia suicide statistics">[http://www.who.int/mental_health/media/russ.pdf WHO Russia suicide statistics] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/6HVSC5CuD?url=http://www.who.int/mental_health/media/russ.pdf |date=20130620021839 |dateformat=iso }} [[WHO|WHO]] retrieved on March 21, 2008</ref>。2007年，約22％的自殺者為40至49歲，男性自殺者比女自殺者多近6倍<ref>[http://en.rian.ru/society/20080131/98094233.html One million people commit suicide every year globally] {{Wayback|url=http://en.rian.ru/society/20080131/98094233.html |date=20130515193455 }} [[RIA_Novosti|RIA Novosti]] Retrieved on March 21, 2008</ref>。

於2012年，俄羅斯的青少年自殺率比世界平均水平高出三倍<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/04/20/world/europe/in-russia-spate-of-teenage-suicides-causes-alarm.html?_r=0|title=A Spate of Teenage Suicides Alarms Russians|last=Kates|first=Glenn|date=19 April 2012|publisher=The New York Times|accessdate=30 January 2013|archive-date=2017-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170307142022/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/04/20/world/europe/in-russia-spate-of-teenage-suicides-causes-alarm.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 和酒精的關係 ==
大量使用[[酒精|酒精]]是自殺問題的顯著因素，估計一半的自殺是由濫用酒精所引致的<ref name="Heavy Drinking and Suicide in Russia"/><ref name="demoscope.ru">[http://demoscope.ru/weekly/2010/0427/analit05.php Demoscope - Demographic, social and economic consequences of alcohol abuse in Russia] {{Wayback|url=http://demoscope.ru/weekly/2010/0427/analit05.php |date=20120521185847 }} [[Demoscope|Demoscope]] Retrieved on July 6, 2010</ref>；由於90年代中期俄羅斯人的人均酒精使用量下降，雖然當時俄羅斯面臨經濟危機，但俄羅斯的自殺率亦一直穩步下降<ref name="demoscope.ru"/>。

